This paper deals with the optimization of wireless coverage using a UAV, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed algorithm uses particle swarm optimization, which is a common optimization technique in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the optimization problem can be framed as a machine learning problem, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
